title: ET Tried To Call Home. Then He Called Us
posting_body: ['ET Tried To Call Home.', 'Then He Called Us', 'Price: $2,400', 'Property Type: Apartment', 'Bedrooms: 1.0', 'Bathrooms: 1.0', 'Pets: Pets OK', 'Building Amenities', 'Doorman', 'Laundry', 'Apartment Amenities', 'Dishwasher', 'Hardwood', 'Renovated', 'Marble Bath', 'Granite Kitchen', 'Microwave', 'Stainless Steel Appliances', 'City View', "When Walking into this unit that has a Spacious Layout you're Welcomed with Beautiful Hardwood Flooring, Knee to Ceiling Windows allowing all the Natural Lighting you need as well as High Ceilings.", 'Once ready for Dinner Time Cook with Elegance in your Fully Custom Marble Kitchen that Features White Cabinetry, Granite Countertops and Stainless Steel Appliances.', 'End your night with a smile and wash away all your problems in your white marble bathroom with soaking tub and custom vanity.', '-Pictures used for references-', '~Amenities~', '- Laundry Room in building', '- Elevators - Pet friendly', '- Whole Foods is 15 min walk away & they deliver to the doorman for a flat $5 dollar fee.', '~The Neighborhood~', 'Located in the heart of the Financial District, within walking distance of the Fulton train station giving you easy access to the A,C,2,3,4,5,J,Z make any destination in the city a quick trip.', 'It is also conveniently surrounded by shopping centers, fine dining and amazing entertainment destinations.', '~Contact~', 'Daniel Bernabe', '929 928 5855', 'Any Questions Do Not Hesitate To Call Or Text Me At Anytime']
